{"tid":429453,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[情境題]後生仔唔捱得?","createTime":"2017-10-09T02:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T06:31:35.000Z","uid":103187,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"36f4bcdd71eefc2c9bfaa384bfbf836eff40b7ee","tid":429453,"uid":103187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"我今年畢業出黎打份牛工<br />\n點知入到間大公司個文化同人事都好唔友善<br />\n由於我仲係試用期頭一個月 所以要跟師<br />\n師傅佢頭一兩日講完啲入門嘅嘢<br />\n轉個頭佢就要我識晒啲深嘢 <br />\n我一話未識可唔可以示範一次佢就閪起塊面<br />\n問我啲客滿意我地嘅服務下次會再黎呢樣嘢叫咩<br />\n我直接答佢「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪顧客會回頭囉 」<br />\n佢就用好似我錯嘅口吻話「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇搞錯啊你 係Return customer啊」<br />\n我口講唔好意思唔好意思 心諗「屌你老母我有講錯咩」<br />\n後來仲要突登跣我 點我去做錯嘢之後過黎冷嘲熱諷咁<br />\n再到前一個禮拜 我一日訓少好幾個鐘<br />\n係屋企熟讀我自己抄嘅筆記終於融會貫通諗住實冇死啦 <br />\n點知佢直接係成Team人面前講話 <br />\n「叻晒啦 之後仲有好多嘢唔洗我教啦」<br />\n佢有教過但我唔記得咪認衰仔囉<br />\n但係冇教唔識又屌 教完熟讀又屌 到底想點<br />\n<br />\n到呢幾日我覺得條友係搵我黎過橋<br />\n話就話比機會我試下做 <br />\n實質我係前線做到冇停手 佢係櫃枱玩手機<br />\n聽番比較好人的同事講番<br />\n我係前線做到死下死下條友攞晒啲功勞上身<br />\n仲要周圍唱我做好少嘢 好似要封殺我咁<br />\n叫其他人夠膽就答我問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到想搵個釘書機都冇人應我<br />\n我應該點做?<br />\n<br />\n第一次發表文章 有錯唔好屌咁大力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辭職啦 仲諗啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番工係咁架啦 樓豬收皮啦"},{"pid":"7635aa27f2cdbb34ae0068d14412e7c12186c7b3","tid":429453,"uid":103187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:20:02.000Z","msg":"求高人指點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dea453dc96bc682aa0669104f5c5eaf7a25fd05","tid":429453,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"走啦 同佢有親咩"},{"pid":"61175eb7e87d225ebb68bd82cd0ccb694c77152e","tid":429453,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:26:23.000Z","msg":"走啦，遇著個仆街<br />\n<br />\n到時問你做咩走就照直講<br />\n<br />\n可能會留你，轉你去第二到做/ 跟另一個"},{"pid":"80e685e1437ce1a8d671be5511fc6f75dfaced18","tid":429453,"uid":7744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:29:32.000Z","msg":"同我第一次返工差唔多..<br />\n似乎已經變左文化"},{"pid":"fab1c45fe032b7b8fe10a91f8e0d14404b2efb8a","tid":429453,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"大把機會，走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ada3ac067e487dad0cf5143fc52318e6bedea73","tid":429453,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"辭職再去HR 投訴<br />\n最少佢個底都花左先"},{"pid":"74c2176c076053b9e49a88f1478e549c06bf8e8a","tid":429453,"uid":55391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:52:10.000Z","msg":"你份工教英文架？"},{"pid":"5525c3703986255425fbc979f87497eedcc60d9c","tid":429453,"uid":142894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"搵定後路先，然後屌佢一獲先走"},{"pid":"df7079d35c8245140888861acd907afa8d224d8e","tid":429453,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"Return customer 啊~~~~~~~~~"},{"pid":"dea7cb6318ded3cd7f7ebd25620debf68d4fce71","tid":429453,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"真係要靠份糧比自己洗就騎牛搵馬啦<br />\n唔洗靠份糧直接辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b719d29bb72da24c4fb1f62575a76e9f463b75e6","tid":429453,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係要靠份糧比自己洗就騎牛搵馬啦<br />\n唔洗靠份糧直接辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"85fb314507ce525a80bf6e44c894a2c3ec42f901","tid":429453,"uid":52474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"開公司名 跟手遞信走人"},{"pid":"9d8cd93a64080